%@4@%%@AB@%Specifying Default Library Names%@AE@%%@EH@%%@NL@%
%@NL@%
SETUP normally gives each combined library a name of the form %@AI@%m%@AE@%LIBC%@AI@%fs%@AE@%.LIB,
where %@AI@%m%@AE@% is S, M ,C, or L (memory model); %@AI@%f%@AE@% is A, E, or 7 (math library); and
